  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Sales Engineer, Power Electronics",
  "description": "<ul><li>Provide technical sales support for AC and DC power sources and power systems across local and overseas markets (This is not a pure-sales/hunter role)</li><li>Support customers on product development, customization, and technical modifications to meet application needs.</li><li>Deliver technical and product training to sales teams, customers, and distributors to strengthen product knowledge and usage.</li><li>Work closely with sales and marketing teams to support sales objectives and customer engagements.</li><li>Collaborate with internal teams, factories, distributors, and customers to ensure effective technical support and solution delivery.</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Minimum 1-3 years of Application/Technical Sales experience (can be in Product-Sales or Service-Sales function)</li><li>Diploma/NITEC and above in Electronic/Electrical, Mechatronics or relevant Engineering discipline</li></ul><p>If the role resonates with you and your professional experience complements the responsibilities listed, send your resume to <strong>koh.dickson@bayesrecruitment.com</strong><br /><br />Dickson KOH, EA Registration R1103367<br />www.bayesrecruitment.com</p>",
